In order to access the Apache Tomcat Server from external machine, edit the file:

vi /etc/tomcat9/tomcat-users.xml   ---> In case of Ubuntu 22.04

vi /etc/tomcat/tomcat-users.xml    ----> In case of CentOS 7


<role rolename="admin-gui,manager-gui,manager-script,manager-jmx,manager-status,admin-gui"/>
<user username="tomubuntu" password="ubuntu" roles="admin-gui,manager-gui,manager-script"/>
